hotel.name: Hotel 81 Osaka
hotel.description: Ibis Novena is located at the corner of Irrawaddy & Balestier road. It is near Novena train station, Zhongshan Park, Mount Elizabeth Novena & Tan Tock Seng Hospital. The first International 3-star hotel in Novena, a short walk to several Shopping Malls &2 train stops to Orchard road. It features 241 stylish designed rooms ideal for single, double or triple occupants, free WiFi internet access, restaurant & bar and free parking. Provides Free shuttle to Novena train station & Orchard upon request.
